title: BREAKING: Sutton United reserve goalkeeper Wayne Shaw RESIGNS after FA Cup pie stunt
text:
DS 
The keeper was pictured eating a pie during Sutton's 2-0 defeat to Arsenal in The FA Cup last night. Wayne Shaw eats a pie during Sutton's defeat to Arsenal Tuesday, 21st February 2017 WAYNE SHAW was snapped eating a pie while on the substitutes' bench for Sutton last night. 1 / 7
